restaurant opens
at start of restaurant activities...
-generate customers
-distribute customers across 5 tables randomly

-randomly select waiter
-randomly selected waiter selects table to approach
-waiter randomly picks customer to serve
-customer places order
-waiter takes order to kitchen to process
-kitchen processes order 
-kitchen signals waiter
-waiter serves customer
-customer eats food
-customer pays for food
-customer leaves restaurant

NOTE: states of a waiter include the following:
- states =>free, engaged
- history of orders
- walks over to a chosen table
- takes order from randomly chosen customer
- takes order to the kitchen
- brings processed order from kitchen to customer
- serves customer
- leaves
- receives payment when customer finishes eating

a list of orders served by restaurant with their respective price tags
can calculate sales in a day for restaurant